It does work in Win 7 64x just right click the exe and go to properties and on the compatibility tab check the Windows XP SP3 as well as Run as administrator check boxes. Without doing that the game seems to crash after a few levels of gameplay.

Oh, also if the installer says cannot find "blank" then just delete the installer and re-extract it from the torrent again. It worked for me.
